active-flow-timeout.help: Timeout to report active flows (60 - 3600 sec, default = 1800).
active-flow-timeout.name: active-flow-timeout

inactive-flow-timeout.help: Timeout for periodic report of finished flows (10 - 600 sec, default = 15).
inactive-flow-timeout.name: inactive-flow-timeout

interface.help: Specify outgoing interface to reach server.
interface.name: interface

interface-select-method.help: Specify how to select outgoing interface to reach server.
interface-select-method.name: interface-select-method

options.help: Set outgoing interface by SD-WAN or policy routing rules.
options.name: sdwan

source-ip.help: Source IP address for communication with the NetFlow agent.
source-ip.name: source-ip

template-tx-counter.help: Counter of flowset records before resending a template flowset record.
template-tx-counter.name: template-tx-counter

template-tx-timeout.help: Timeout for periodic template flowset transmission (60 - 86400 sec, default = 1800).
template-tx-timeout.name: template-tx-timeout
